    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107000/extras/97b5e2a50e83919741156abe50c29f6e.poster.avif?t=1769090428\" width=1170 height=473 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107000/extras/97b5e2a50e83919741156abe50c29f6e.webm?t=1769090428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是埃伦要塞的铸剑师，冷硬的钢铁经你之手会变成比黄金更珍贵的利器。顾客们怀揣金币而来，诉说着他们的需求，只为寻求一柄致命精准、完美平衡且优雅绝伦的武器。在这座存世无几的文明灯塔中满足他们的要求，打磨你的技艺。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107000/extras/d56354749019d76e6ecb1da332654062.webp?t=1769090428\" width=1560 height=56 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开启《铸剑吟》的故事模式。游玩《铸剑吟》战役模式的第一个章节，抵达人类最后的数座避风港之一——埃伦要塞，为营地中的难民打造剑刃，探索失落之城的废墟。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一窥创意模式的样貌，初步体验《铸剑吟》的铸剑沙盒系统，接触其中海量的工具、部件与材料。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107000/extras/830312489a2aa1ed8d30bda75ece338c.poster.avif?t=1769090428\" width=1170 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107000/extras/830312489a2aa1ed8d30bda75ece338c.webm?t=1769090428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107000/extras/49cb643a1da98ad8666f3bee62462aa6.webp?t=1769090428\" width=1560 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用自由刀刃塑形与精细的模块化锻造系统，随心打造你心中的理想利剑。创造任意世界的武器，风格囊括从东方到西方，从历史经典到奇幻神兵，每一处细节都可以自定义，每一个部件都精雕细琢，尽显匠心。探索《铸剑吟》庞大的刻纹与部件系统，在金属、皮革与木材等多种原料中尽情采择。每一件作品皆独一无二。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107000/extras/ccbe1eafb45a69b4234a6d3316bcd066.poster.avif?t=1769090428\" width=1170 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107000/extras/ccbe1eafb45a69b4234a6d3316bcd066.webm?t=1769090428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107000/extras/5730e74db2c5438069215cad15ec05ed.webp?t=1769090428\" width=1560 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >承接来自战士、贵族与雇佣兵的委托。根据真实物理原理平衡剑刃的种种属性，满足顾客各自的需求与期望。掌握刀刃弧度塑形与雕刻技艺，搜集稀有材料，扩充你的剑身部件库。</p>",
